{
  "stem": "9446.2",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I mean there was no danger there at all, because it was far from the  front line, from Germany.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Over there, in Penza, I was working there as-- I don't even remember what kinds of-- some sort of slave jobs.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But our lives were not threatened the same way as they were threatened under the Nazis.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You  know what I mean?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There was no political-- anything like that.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But we were just hungry.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we had to do a task, which even people who are well-fed could hardly put up with.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "What can I tell you?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Did you to-- did you try to keep in touch with your father?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, I was, but there was no contact.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Absolutely nothing.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Maybe the mail didn't even get through.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I don't believe-- would the Germans care about, you know, enabling one Jew to contact another Jew?",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That was out of the question.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Now, that was my time between 1939 and '40.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Actually, it was about a year I spent there  in Penza.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Then I never gave up on the idea of reaching my father somehow.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I said to myself, I have to get out from this part of Russia.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Maybe I will find a way of going back to Poland.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I found a way to go back to Poland, but not to Warsaw, of course.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I wanted to be as close as I possibly could to Warsaw, which is a town, again, in Belarus, Bialystok.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Why Bialystok?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because I had an aunt in Bialystok.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "She was a sister of my mother, who was working in a clinic.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "What was her name?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Her name was Renia, which is, in Polish spelling, is R-E-N-I-A.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She was assisting the doctors there.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
